# Original Idea

Add support for agents -- synthesize agent templates using reference projects (opencode, codex, etc in ~/src/ or ~/src/pag-server/ref-projects/), search online for best templates for planning, coding, etc, use the relevant `better-*` skills, and add these as builtins. We need to support user-supplied agent templates too.

